Throughout this iteration I worked mainly on my next 5 user stories which I will outline below.
I attempted some scraping of promotions and tesco but they remain to be blocked and difficult
to obtain.

User story 21 - Choose preferred store/retailer:
allows users to set preferred store and lock it in place so their products come up, steps below
1. User logs in or continues as guest
2. click search on navbar
3. select store region from dropdown in nav and set as preferred store
4. go in between pages of the system to see that stores items will still appear

User story 22: Save and load baskets
allow users to save their favourite baskets they build with a name and load it to existing basket, steps below
1. User logs in with username
2. click search on navbar
3. build a basket
4. click see full basket in navbar
5. give it a name and click save
6. click view full basket and load basket to existing basket or delete saved basket completely

User story 23: Use a basket template:
Similar to save basket, allows users to build a starter template basket
1. User logs in with username
2. click search on navbar
3. build a basket and click see full basket in navbar
4. give it a name and click save
5. to use as a template ensure existing basket is empty
6. click start and it will load to basket or click delete from templates

User story 24: Add from past baskets
Allow users to add specific products from past baskets to current basket
1. user logs in with username
2. click search on navbar
3. click see full basket
4. click view saved basket
5. click view items on saved basket
6. add specific products to current basket

User story 25: Favourite items to add
allows users build a page of their favourite products
1. User logs in with username
2. click search on navbar
3. click favourite button specific to products
4. click view favourites in navbar
5. add favourites to current basket or remove from favourites page

